## U.S. Treasury OFAC Sanctions Lists

**Provider:** U.S. Department of the Treasury, Office of Foreign Assets Control (OFAC)
**Datasets:** Specially Designated Nationals (SDN) List, Consolidated Non-SDN List
**Portal:** https://ofac.treasury.gov/
**Download:**
  - SDN: https://www.treasury.gov/ofac/downloads/sdn.csv
  - Consolidated: https://www.treasury.gov/ofac/downloads/consolidated/cons_prim.csv

### License

OFAC sanctions data is a work of the United States Government and is in the
**public domain** under 17 U.S.C. §105. No copyright restrictions apply.

### Attribution (good practice)

> Includes sanctions data from the U.S. Department of the Treasury,
> Office of Foreign Assets Control (OFAC).
> https://ofac.treasury.gov/

### Implementation Notes

- **Source module:** `periphery/ingest/sources/ofac_sanctions.py` — license noted in module docstring.
- **API responses:** `attribution`, `license`, and `source_url` fields are included in all
  API responses that return OFAC-sourced documents or entities.
- **Frontend:** Listed in `DataSourcesFooter` component.

